rows.name:
Hey, have you ever tried
Beat Paste Paratha?

rows.label: tlk41100123_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Paratha is a staple food in Gula,
but if you mix in some mashed
Beat Shrimp, it's extra delicious!

rows.label: tlk41100123_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't know where this Liberalitas
place is, but it must be a great place
if people come up with stuff like this!

rows.label: tlk41100123_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I want to go there with Sanema someday
and try some fresh Beat Shrimp
cooked by the pros!
